@node INTRO "Introduction"
 We've all deleted files and then been able to recover them using a utility
 such as DiskSalv. Quite a relief most of the time... but what if the files
 must be unrecoverable? Use Erase!
 
                 @{" USE THIS PROGRAM WITH EXTREME CAUTION " link DISCLAIM}
@endnode
